   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>A brother once studied the word calling.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>He put several dozen verses together and grouped them into ten sections.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>For illustration, I will list them in the following sections: Section One The source of our calling: The primary source God 1 Thes 2:12 .</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>The intermediary source Jesus Christ Rom 1:6 .</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Section Two The called ones: Scope general all men 1 Cor 1:24 .</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Scope spiritual sinners Luke 5:32 .</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>God's valuation vessels of mercy Rom 9:23-24 .</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Actual condition not many who are wise 1 Cor 1:26 .</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Section Three The goal of our calling: Repentance Luke 5:32 .</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Salvation 2 Thes 2:13-14 .</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Peace Col 3:15 .</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>Light 1 Pet 2:9 .</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Fellowship 1 Cor 1:9 .</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Service Rom 1:1 .</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Freedom Gal 5:13 .</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>Holiness 1 Cor 1:2 .</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>Suffering 1 Pet 2:21 .</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>Eternal life 1 Tim 6:12 .</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>Eternal inheritance Heb 9:15 .</S>
   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>Eternal glory 1 Pet 5:10 .</S>
   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>Section Four The principle of calling: According to God's plan Rom 8:28 .</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>According to God's grace 2 Tim 1:9 .</S>
   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>Not according to man's merit 2 Tim 1:9 .</S>
   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>Section Five The sphere of our calling: In the Lord 1 Cor 7:22 .</S>
   <S PAR='25' RSNT='1' SNO='25'>In grace Gal 1:6 .</S>
   <S PAR='26' RSNT='1' SNO='26'>In peace 1 Cor 7:15 .</S>
   <S PAR='27' RSNT='1' SNO='27'>In sanctification 1 Thes 4:7 .</S>
   <S PAR='28' RSNT='1' SNO='28'>In one Body Col 3:15 .</S>
   <S PAR='29' RSNT='1' SNO='29'>Section Six The way we are called: Through the gospel 2 Thes 2:14 .</S>
   <S PAR='30' RSNT='1' SNO='30'>Through God's grace Gal 1:15 .</S>
   <S PAR='31' RSNT='1' SNO='31'>Through God's glory 2 Pet 1:3 .</S>
   <S PAR='32' RSNT='1' SNO='32'>Through the divine nature 2 Pet 1:3 .</S>
   <S PAR='33' RSNT='1' SNO='33'>Section Seven The nature of our calling: Holy 2 Tim 1:9 .</S>
   <S PAR='34' RSNT='1' SNO='34'>From above Phil 3:14 .</S>
   <S PAR='35' RSNT='1' SNO='35'>Heavenly Heb 3:1 .</S>
   <S PAR='36' RSNT='1' SNO='36'>Humble 1 Cor 1:26 .</S>
   <S PAR='37' RSNT='1' SNO='37'>Section Eight The requirements for our calling: Remaining in it 1 Cor 7:20, 24 .</S>
   <S PAR='38' RSNT='1' SNO='38'>Walking according to it 1 Cor 7:17 .</S>
   <S PAR='39' RSNT='1' SNO='39'>Counted worthy of it Eph 4:1 .</S>
   <S PAR='40' RSNT='1' SNO='40'>Counted worthy of the God who calls us 1 Thes 2:12 .</S>
   <S PAR='41' RSNT='1' SNO='41'>Being diligent 2 Pet 1:10 .</S>
   <S PAR='42' RSNT='1' SNO='42'>Section Nine The encouragement of our calling: Hope Eph 1:18; 4:4 .</S>
   <S PAR='43' RSNT='1' SNO='43'>Reward Phil 3:14 .</S>
   <S PAR='44' RSNT='1' SNO='44'>Section Ten The guarantee of our calling: God's nature faithfulness 1 Cor 1:9; 1 Thes 5:24 .</S>
   <S PAR='45' RSNT='1' SNO='45'>God's plan Rom 8:30 .</S>
   <S PAR='46' RSNT='1' SNO='46'>God's grace Rom 11:29 .</S>
   </TEXT>
